{"id": 37, "genre": 1000, "title": "微博推出打赏功能，你怎么看？", "description": "8月7日，微博启动 “打赏”功能公测，自媒体作者开通这一功能后，所发表的文章中会出现打赏按钮，网友可以根据对文章的喜爱程度向作者支付一定的费用。", "record_count": 2662, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": null, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606161907cN6lGxzrqLW7483D.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-08-12T16:27:43Z", "questions": [{"id": 56, "title": "微博推出打赏功能，你怎么看？", "content": "微博推出打赏功能，你怎么看？", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 512, "content": "我觉得专业文章被打赏大概有难度", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161733VSkOuywWAc6r0vo5.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 513, "content": "写东西好挣钱啊，我也去写个玄幻小说什么的！", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161733OcyjBRpmKPxlYJCd.png", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 514, "content": "我开一个“我是怎么被自己蠢死的”会有人打赏我吗", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161733u18j4FBlUGfMeqAs.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 515, "content": "喜欢那种“来！给爷笑一个！”的爽感", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161733jSftpH3RFuElsBmC.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 516, "content": "感觉陆琪要发财了", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161733UvGr9AOSpZe5KFRl.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 517, "content": "不懂你们在说什么", "image": "img/option/option/20160606161733DRjNtwGeWcfqMzVZ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}